{"tid":1345553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗打手 辛苦曬啦","createTime":"2019-07-22T02:19:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T02:33:14.000Z","uid":192581,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c8869c6897a9e78331d74589294b8d26fdbcd0c4","tid":1345553,"uid":192581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:19:04.000Z","msg":"你班黑社會無貢獻憑乜撚嘢打良民? <br />\n你班仆街黑社會著乜撚嘢白衫??? 洗白?<br />\n同何君妖握手?你以為人地真係重視你?<br />\n依家港島示威有阻到你吸毒?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔該你班0貢獻既垃圾死返個去臭閪村竇到啦 <br />\n無差別追打手無寸鐵既良民 更甚牽連孕婦細路<br />\n你以為自己係邊個? 你憑乜撚嘢叫自己香港人?<br />\n<br />\n啊係喎對唔住 唔記得咗警察成立咗新部門<br />\n叫做<strong>警黑社會</strong><br />\n哎呀唔好意思 唔好意思<br />\n辛苦曬啦手足 你地收公俸出全力 做足場面<br />\n我仲怪錯咗你<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">放心 由今日開始 你將享有與黑警同等既支持</span><br />\n經已同所有良好市民解釋咗<br />\n以後我地良民將全力尊重同善待你<br />\n就好似我地對黑警一樣<br />\n你所做既好事 必<strong>銘記於心</strong> <strong>必定回報</strong> <br />\n<br />\n話是話<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今日既手足同我出曬黎去元朗同港島線涼冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家仲未見坐爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">手足辛苦曬 我地既抗爭一定會開花結果 記住唔好分化 互通資訊<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"7d559d47c2dfa63b8b41583f7a6254cbb30a6ba0","tid":1345553,"uid":192581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:22:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a88d995033872401c9e1248568f351f7ad87ef5","tid":1345553,"uid":192581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:22:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"982b61aa8538cb3968189fdb3c31534cd00844af","tid":1345553,"uid":192581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:25:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df3a223c05bea08915314e6ff2c5faab465a12b6","tid":1345553,"uid":192581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,